{
  "stem": "1736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Within Austria.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "G-R-A-Z.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you like, you can look it up after.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there, again, we were met by-- an organized-- like, and organized into a group, which we had already-- but by a guide.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this guide, his job was to try and get us across the border-- that is, the Austrian border-- into Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now this is December, 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's winter time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's cold, and something happened there--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a leather jacket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- something happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were two guides, and I think one of them disappeared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyway, that doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went with our guide and we started--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "12.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we started walking, and we walked for not only days but weeks, you know, in the Alps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this guy used to take us-- and he had connections.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would find-- talk to farms that used to be up and he used to know huts where we could stay overnight.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a question of just getting across the Alps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We finally got to the German border, and then he had to work out a time, because the border guards were changing at certain times and the thing was to get across the border when the change of guard was taking place.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, from the border, you would get in-- we were told and it was so-- we would get into an area which was called a no man's land.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know exactly how deep it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we had-- the second thing is to get into the Yugoslav, or Croatian, side border.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were, of course, on the lookout for people as well, because they didn't want to have these people in their country.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
